        </div>
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-center my-5">Dono</h2>
    <div class="divAutores">
        <div class="sobreAutores">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12 col-lg-4">
                    <img src="~/images/perfilAutora.jpg" alt="Autor">
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-lg-8 textoSobre">
                    <h2>Lorena Melo</h2>
                    <p>
                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Explicabo, deleniti est? Delectus esse dolore at
                        corrupti aspernatur libero maiores! Est obcaecati inventore deleniti enim? Perspiciatis, aperiam veniam.
